        "text": "<p>Unlike traditional infant formula, EDUCA Organics Ultra Premium Formula are specifically designed for active individuals on-the-go. With proven, hard-working strains that are crafted to boost your performance, streamline your system, and help you achieve your full potential. </p><p>Where's your nutrition going to take you today?</p>"
