      "settings": {
        "subtitle": "Active culture formulas",
        "title": "We formulate for key performance areas",
        "text": "<p>Our bodies are incredible machines. But push them too hard, and things can get a bit wonky. That’s why athletic individuals are particularly prone to various issues (think: immune suppression, colds, gastrointestinal upset, bloating, and mental health stress, among others). These are the  exact areas that EDUCA Organics Ultra Premium Formula are designed to target. It's a bit like having your own miniature infant nutrition pit crew, working hard to keep you in the race and ahead of the pack.</p>",
